<H2>
Our Halkomelem Language Materials</H2>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://www.native-languages.org/halkomelem_words.htm
">Halkomelem Vocabulary</a></b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Our list of vocabulary words in Halkomelem, with comparison to words in other Salishan languages.
<BR>

<H2>
Halkomelem Language Lessons and Linguistic Descriptions</H2>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://web.uvic.ca/hrd/hulq/
">Introduction to Hul'q'umi'num'</a></b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Online Halkomelem language information including pronunciation and spelling, grammar, and dialect differences.
<BR>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://www.sfu.ca/halk-ethnobiology/
">Halkomelem Ethnobiology</a></b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Compendium of information about native Halkomelem plants and animals, with their original names. 
<BR>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://www.ydli.org/langs/halkomelem.htm
">First Nations Languages of British Columbia: Halkomelem</a></b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Profile and linguistic bibliography of Halkomelem from the Yinka Dene Language Institute.
<BR>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://www.languagegeek.com/salishan/halkomelem.html
">Halq'emeylem</a></b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Halkomelem orthography and text example.
<BR>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://www.ufv.ca/calendar/2009_10/ProgramsF-L/IS_STOLO.htm
">Sto:lo Studies</a>:</b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
A Sto:lo language and culture program offered by the University College of the Fraser Valley.
<BR>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://www.languagegeek.com/nwc/nwc_keyboards.html
">North West Coast Keyboards</a>:</b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Fonts and keyboard map including the special symbols used by Halkomelem and other Pacific Northwest languages.
<BR>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://multitree.org/codes/hur.html
">Halkomelem Language Tree</a>:</b> <br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Theories about Halkomelem's language relationships compiled by Linguist List.
<BR>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://wals.info/languoid/lect/wals_code_hlk
">Halkomelem Language Structures</a>:</b> <br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Upriver Halkomelem linguistic profile and academic bibliography.
<BR>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"  ALT="*"><B><A HREF="
http://curtis.library.northwestern.edu/curtis/viewPage.cgi?showp=1&size=2&id=nai.09.book.00000271&volume=9#nav
">Coast Salish Comparative Vocabulary</a>:</b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Early 20th-century wordlists of Cowichan and other Salishan languages.
<BR>

<h2>
Halkomelem Language Preservation and Usage
</h2>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://www.canada.com/chilliwacktimes/news/story.html?id=ff6a8dc1-0f22-48f7-9c89-9d6452aaed6b
">Sto:lo Language in the Classroom</a>:</b> <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
News article on Halq'ameylem language revival among the Sto:lo tribes.
<BR>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://home.istar.ca/~bthom/icsnl2002-edited.htm
">Hulquminum Language Revitalization</a>:</b> <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Interviews and analyses about the survival of Cowichan Halkomelem.
<BR>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://www.ethnologue.com/show_language.asp?code=hur
">Halkomelem</a></b> <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Demographic information about the Halkomelem language from the Ethnologue of Languages.
<BR>

